{"tid":2032345,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果香港人都移民台灣，豈不「鵲巢溝占」？","createTime":"2020-05-24T04:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T19:34:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"01a6377bbe6c02ebdd5d1cfcc48722c86d3973ce","tid":2032345,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"如果香港人都移民，豈不「鵲巢溝占」？<br />\n<br />\n不過香港人真的決定避禍，留得青山在，港人就是香港最大的資產。<br />\n<br />\n無奈台灣真的太小了，無法容得下太多人口。並且港人文化其實跟台灣未必契合。<br />\n<br />\n但是如果香港人都分散到世界各地，以後就很難有凝聚力。也無法再傳承港人的文化、精神。<br />\n<br />\n我的建議是，澳洲目前是一塊地廣人稀的土地，並且澳洲當年本來就是大英帝國🇬🇧向外開拓出的新大陸。<br />\n<br />\n香港人融入很多英文化，如果港人可以在澳洲選擇一塊區域，集中移民到那裏，重新建立新香港 #NirvanaHK<br />\n相信香港人做得到。<br />\n<br />\n大家怎麼看？"},{"pid":"38760c0a704921cd9d32d2a0eb4b2ad1557f5d01","tid":2032345,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:21:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1152252624856410/permalink/3029031287178525/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1152252624856410%2Fpermalink%2F3029031287178525%2F&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtfCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=6c107fea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/1152252624856410/permalink/3029031287178525/</a>"},{"pid":"5e571f7e45eefba976400598e6876f62697e5961","tid":2032345,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:22:57.000Z","msg":"如果香港人都移民 《 依個假設已經係唔可能"},{"pid":"30267ad0df33f2b88cf19d3b6dc50533da803678","tid":2032345,"uid":46500,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:26:45.000Z","msg":"剩係一個台中已經係香港嘅兩倍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且到時移民嘅只會係恐共嘅人 奶共果班會留低"},{"pid":"b00c4dee96a71f3ccae1805efd4c200f17f556c3","tid":2032345,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:37:35.000Z","msg":"何不去加拿大？"},{"pid":"b1fd9240bd9207139a3cc9e3f6fe2203857efaae","tid":203